snippet.title: Gore Doctor - Demo Walkthrough with commentary! Horror game available now on Steam!
snippet.description:
We are thrilled to announce that the chilling world of Gore Doctor is now at your fingertips thanks to the demo available on Steam! Dive headfirst into the heart-pounding terror as you test your nerves in our gruesome horror game! 

Check out the demo and make sure to wishlist!

Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2495990/Gore_Doctor/

Experience the spine-tingling anticipation as you step into the dark, mysterious school transformed into a mental healthcare facility where unimaginable horrors await. Gore Doctor brings you into a realm of blood-curdling fear, where every corner hides a new nightmare.

🚧 Work in Progress Disclaimer 🚧

Please be aware that what you'll encounter in the demo is a work in progress. We're hard at work crafting an even more terrifying and immersive experience for the full release. Your feedback and suggestions will be invaluable in shaping the final product, so we encourage you to share your thoughts with us in the community section - thank you!
